    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1907-06-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1907-06-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="328"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d328">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3294/29.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul-General <persName type="from">Skinner</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate-General</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Marseilles</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-06-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 8, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Jacobs’s imprisonment continues, although extradition authorized March 30.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Skinner.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
